00:23:21.230 --> 00:23:23.650
Kochira <i>e</i> Iai-Iai-Iai.

00:23:25.820 --> 00:23:31.610
<i>Woh... mirakuru ZENKAI pawaa!</i>

00:23:33.620 --> 00:23:35.290
<i>Hara heri wanpaku kinto un.</i>

00:23:35.490 --> 00:23:37.370
<i>Yama hodo takusan suiheisen.</i>

00:23:37.580 --> 00:23:39.460
<i>Deatte wakarete deatte wakarete.</i>

00:23:39.660 --> 00:23:41.290
Ta-i-he-n.

00:23:41.500 --> 00:23:47.090
<i>Ah mou Kamisama mo tsurai yo ne!</i>

00:23:47.300 --> 00:23:49.260
<i>Gomen.</i>

00:23:49.470 --> 00:23:54.550
<i>Woh... manpuku ZENKAI pawaa!</i>

00:23:57.270 --> 00:24:02.520
<i>Dete koi tobikiri ZENKAI pawaa!</i>
